Cybersecurity involves  protecting  individuals, organizations and governments from digital attacks by protecting systems and data from unauthorized use or harm.
## Levels of protection
a) Individual : safeguard your identity and  personal data,
b)Organization: responsibility to protect the organization’s data and customers.
c) Government :  protection becomes even more important at the government level, where national security, economic stability and the safety and wellbeing of citizens are at stake
